Sentencas: Direct internal reforming (DIR) operation of solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) reduces system complexity, improves system efficiency but increases the risk of carbon deposition which can reduce the system performance and durability.
Titulo: Coupling deep learning and multi-objective genetic algorithms to achieve high performance and durability of direct internal reforming solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: In this study, a novel framework that combines a multi-physics model, deep learning, and multiobjective optimization algorithms is proposed for improving SOFC performance and minimizing carbon deposition.
Titulo: Coupling deep learning and multi-objective genetic algorithms to achieve high performance and durability of direct internal reforming solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The sensitive operating parameters are identified by performing a global sensitivity analysis.
Titulo: Coupling deep learning and multi-objective genetic algorithms to achieve high performance and durability of direct internal reforming solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The results of parameter analysis highlight the effects of overall temperature distribution and methane flux on carbon deposition.
Titulo: Coupling deep learning and multi-objective genetic algorithms to achieve high performance and durability of direct internal reforming solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: It is also found that the reduction of carbon deposition is accompanied by a decrease in cell performance.
Titulo: Coupling deep learning and multi-objective genetic algorithms to achieve high performance and durability of direct internal reforming solid oxide fuel cell
